             was indicted for <rs id="t17880625-4-off18" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17880625-4-off18" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880625-4-off18" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17880625-4-cd19" type="crimeDate">26th day of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880625-4-off18 t17880625-4-cd19"></join>, one piece of silk, for handkerchiefs, containing in length seven yards, value 20 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880625-4-victim93" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Jones
                  <interp inst="t17880625-4-victim93" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
